text: Novourtayevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Starobaishevsky Selsoviet, Dyurtyulinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 136 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 30 km from Dyurtyuli, 11 km from Starobaishevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Dyurtyulinsky District
title: Novourtayevo
